children.name: Rules
children.text:
This twisted old wooden trident is a +1 weapon. 
Once per day, as a bonus action, the wielder can cast Barkskin on themselves.
Once per day, this trident can be transformed into a small raft if it is touching a large enough body of water. This raft can support up to 5 medium creatures. It can be turned back into a trident as an action.
This weapon has advantage against creatures with the ability to breathe water.
